FROM [Products] AS [p]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[TagId], [t2].[Id] AS [Id0], [t2].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [t2].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t2] ON [p1].[TagId] = [t2].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p2] ON [t].[Id] = [p2].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]

FROM (
    SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[BlogCategoryId], [b].[CreateDate], [b].[Description], [b].[Image], [b].[Title]
    FROM [Blogs] AS [b]

    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [b].[Id] AS [Id0], [b].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [b].[Image], [b].[Name] AS [Name0], [c].[Id] AS [Id1], [c].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [c].[Image] AS [Image0], [c].[Name] AS [Name1]

    INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[ColorId], [p0].[CreateDate], [p0].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [c0].[Name]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p2] ON [t].[Id] = [p2].[ProductId]

    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price]

) AS [t]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [b].[Id] AS [Id0], [b].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [b].[Image], [b].[Name] AS [Name0], [c].[Id] AS [Id1], [c].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [c].[Image] AS [Image0], [c].[Name] AS [Name1]

) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [b].[Id], [b].[CreateDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [c].[Id], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreateDate], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsHover], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [b].[Id], [b].[CreateDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [c].[Id], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreateDate], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsHover], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Key], [t].[Id], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t].[Price]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], LTRIM(RTRIM([c].[Name])) AS [Key]

SELECT [t].[Key], [t].[Id], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t].[Price]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], LTRIM(RTRIM([c].[Name])) AS [Key]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
